  "title": "Salesperson #81686",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction (Subcontractor)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Salesperson</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ubi</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 9.00am – 6.00pm; Sat, 9.00am – 1.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $3,000 + Performance Incentive + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop a good understanding of our flooring product range (e.g., carpet tiles, luxury vinyl tiles, laminates, rugs, and others).</li><li>Engage with customers during roadshows and attend international exhibitions when required.</li><li>Learn key product features and selling points, and explain the benefits clearly to customers.</li><li>Build new client relationships through proactive outreach (e.g., cold-calling and walk-ins), and maintain good relationships with existing clients.</li><li>Understand customer needs and recommend suitable solutions.</li><li>Review contract terms and understand how they may impact the company and the customer.</li><li>Communicate clearly and confidently, address customer questions, and support the sales closing process.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Business Studies, Administration, Management, Marketing, or a related field.</li><li>At least 1 year of experience in a sales-related role.</li><li>Able to present product ranges to business partners (e.g., architects, builders, and interior designers).</li><li>Proficient with MS Office and online reporting tools.</li><li>Valid Class 3 driving licence.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81686 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
